							"content:textarea:34:22": {
								"icon": "align-justify",
								"name": "Paragraph",
								"type": "textarea",
								"html": "<p>\n\tAs a member of SAWA, you are among Greenville's most influential and active community leaders, women with a generous spirit and determination to be “doing the most good.\" Meetings are held on the 2nd Wednesday of each month (except July) at 11:30 a.m. at the Kroc Center located at 42 Westfield Street in Greenville (lunch is served).&nbsp;&nbsp;Members have many opportunities throughout the year to volunteer and attend social events and meetings.\n</p>",
